Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Government by the people
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407br5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Jan 1977
President Carter promises a public hotline to the White House aimed at giving more public say on issues. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less